The paper deals with the problem of automatically determining the notability of news stories, which involves natural language processing, machine learning, and information retrieval techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
